elements.containerText: Yappy  Infinite Canvas  Sketch & Architectural Modes  150+ Shape Types  Animations  Effects  Layers

elements.text: Yappy supports sketch and architectural render styles
Infinite canvas with zoom, pan, and viewport culling
Connectors with flow animations (marching ants & dots)
Drop shadows, blend modes, gradients, and opacity
60fps render loop with cached metrics and patterns
Multi-layer support with independent visibility & opacity
